
//- index view

extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the MDN :D
  p
    | Find the tutorial here: 
    a(href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/Server-side/Express_Nodejs', target='_blank') MDN Express Tutorial
    |  and 
    a(href='https://github.com/mdn/express-locallibrary-tutorial', target='_blank') MDN Express Tutorial on GitHub

  h2 Dynamic Content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.book_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies Available:] !{data.book_instance_available_count}
      li #[strong Authors:] !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}
